results.abstract: Seed catalogues are meant to seduce. I prefer the ones that don't set up impossible expectations.
results.snippet: Seed catalogues are meant to seduce. I prefer the ones that don't set up impossible expectations.
results.lead_paragraph: The seed catalogs certainly make it look easy. They turn up every year, ripe with pictures and dreams, when the ground is mean and dead. Each has a distinctive niche: a model for the gardener you imagine you want to be.

headline.main: European Puck: Ak Bars Wins Russian Crown; Karlovy Vary's Czech Title First in 73 Years

results.snippet: Sunday's games in Russia, Switzerland, the Czech Republic, Finland and Germany.
results.lead_paragraph: Alexei Morozov broke a scoreless deadlock with 10 minutes to go in Game 7 of the K.H.L. final, giving Ak Bars Kazan a 1-0 victory over Lokomotiv Yaroslavl on Sunday. The triumph earned the hosts their third Russian championship and the K.H.L.'s first Gagarin Cup, awarded on the 48th anniversary of the flight that made cosmonaut Yuri Gagarin the first man in outer space.
